text: Häggenås SK is a sports club in Häggenås in Sweden. It was established on 2 January 1932. In 1951, the table tennis section was started. The women's soccer team was stared in 1972. The women's soccer played three seasons in the Swedish top division between 1978-1980. ==References== ==Other websites== *Häggenås SK Category:Basketball clubs in Sweden Category:Table tennis clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Ski clubs in Sweden Category:Athletics clubs in Sweden Category:1932 establishments in Sweden
